00:03:04.030 --> 00:03:05.180
And similarly,

00:03:05.205 --> 00:03:07.283
we're going to see this with automobiles.

00:03:07.386 --> 00:03:10.108
A few years after the Wright brothers
figured out flight,

00:03:10.132 --> 00:03:12.304
human beings started using
more and more cars.

00:03:12.328 --> 00:03:13.479
And all of a sudden,

00:03:13.503 --> 00:03:15.789
the regulatory system --
the operating system --

00:03:15.813 --> 00:03:20.387
had to be patched to all of a sudden
address the safety of consumers.

00:03:20.411 --> 00:03:23.538
